data.description: Enjoy this updated townhome in the desirable Farmington Crossing Community! Nestled in a prime location, this one-owner townhome is a true gem. It offers the convenience of being just moments away from Station Park, stores, and quick access to the freeway. Don't forget Lagoon that is just minutes away! The kitchen boasts a suite of high-end appliances that are not only elegant but also highly efficient. New paint and carpet were installed in 2021 along with all of the high-end kitchen appliances and the high-efficiency furnace and air. The HOA offers parks and greenspace, playgrounds, trails, 2 pools, clubhouse and gym. It's easy to enjoy an active lifestyle without leaving your neighborhood!
